

# Requirement -> Create a logger framework to log the errors


- Log Levels -> info , warn , debug , fatal , error
- filtering on the minimum level
- support multiple output -> file, console , cloud
- async logging
- custom configuration


- NFR

Thread Safety
Performance
Extensibility
Maintainbility
Ease of Use


------------------------------------

# Core Entities

loggersystem.multilogger.LogLevel -> enum
LogMessage
loggersystem.multilogger.LogAppender -> Console , file , cloud
LogFormatter -> Simple , JSON
AsyncLogProcessor

# Central Entities

loggersystem.multilogger.Logger -> client
LoggerManager -> Facade
